{
 "name": "RPlog_Monster",
 "title": "Monster",
 "summary": "On a rainy afternoon, the scarred Imperial ambassador Morganna takes a walk with her aides and is approached by the weapons dealer Methos, whom her guards rebuff, and by the soaked, suit-malfunctioning Dracolysk. The friendlier Rodo joins her and the two retreat from the rain to a bar for a meal and small talk about her difficult ambassadorial duties. There the Sarian woman Kaley arrives and quietly proposes that Morganna join her on a 'hunt' -- not of a beast, but of a woman named Jali whom Kaley intends to kill. Drawn by the prospect of violence yet wary of being seen, Morganna agrees only on the condition that she can remain faceless, revealing the predatory cruelty beneath the diplomat's surface.",
